The app is made with the help of tutorial https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m1_ih43p24s

*** Workflow  / Setting up using Vue CLI

https://medium.com/@subodhgarg/how-to-set-up-vue-js-project-in-5-easy-steps-using-vue-cli-669b1aea518b

+ Go into the folder of VueProject and then npm install
+ npm run dev to run the server 


*** If you see there's an error, turn off the server and restart it
